## PagerDuty Alternative

PagerDuty is one of the most recognized platforms for alert routing, escalation policies, and on-call management.

Teams looking for a PagerDuty alternative often want:

- Better early incident triage
- Less manual context gathering
- More help after the page
- A tighter link between alerting and investigation
- More AI support during active incidents

Vibe OnCall includes paging and on-call workflows, but goes beyond alert delivery by helping teams investigate incidents, assemble context across systems, coordinate more effectively, and move toward resolution with specialized AI agents.

